#: ../../talk/files_integration.rst:2
msgid "Files integration"
msgstr "Comhtháthú comhad"

#: ../../talk/files_integration.rst:5
msgid "Talk from Files"
msgstr "Comhrá ó Chomhaid"

#: ../../talk/files_integration.rst:7
msgid ""
"In the Files app, you can chat about files in the sidebar, and even have a "
"call while editing the file. You first have to join the chat."
msgstr ""
"San aip Comhad, is féidir leat comhrá a dhéanamh faoi chomhaid sa bharra "
"taoibh, agus fiú glao a dhéanamh agus an comhad á chur in eagar. Caithfidh "
"tú páirt a ghlacadh sa chomhrá ar dtús."

#: ../../talk/files_integration.rst:17
msgid ""
"You can then chat or have a call with other participants, even when you "
"start editing the file."
msgstr ""
"Ansin is féidir leat comhrá a dhéanamh nó glaoch a bheith agat le "
"rannpháirtithe eile, fiú nuair a thosaíonn tú ag eagarthóireacht an "
"chomhaid."

#: ../../talk/files_integration.rst:22
msgid ""
"In Talk, a conversation will be created for the file. You can chat from "
"there, or go back to the file using the ``...`` menu in the top-right."
msgstr ""
"I Talk, cruthófar comhrá don chomhad. Is féidir leat comhrá a dhéanamh as "
"sin, nó filleadh ar an gcomhad trí úsáid a bhaint as an roghchlár ``...`` sa"
" chúinne uachtarach ar dheis."
